$ $ORACLE_HOME/bin/dbfsize
@ dbfsize

`dbfize` determines → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/database/files/data[database file] type and size:
code {
$ $ORACLE_HOME/bin/dbfsize /opt/oracle/oradata/DB/sysaux01.dbf

Database file: /opt/oracle/oradata/DB/sysaux01.dbf
Database file type: file system
Database file size: 56320 8192 byte blocks
code }

